name: Diabodelite Natural Flavour Multi-Grain Sugar Free Cookies
description: Diabodelite contains low molecular weight fiber- galactomannan which is derived from fenugreek. These fibers in Diabodelite dissolve in water and form a gel to trap carbohydrates thus slowing down their absorption considerably while moving through the digestive tract. As a result, sugar absorbed into the bloodstream is significantly slow, blunting the sharp spike in blood glucose typically experienced by diabetic patients after a meal. As an additional benefit, soluble fibers in Diabodelite have also been shown to lower blood cholesterol, including LDL cholesterol.
